<main class="doc-content">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
        My home network is designed with multiple VLANs, a dedicated firewall,
        a managed switch, and segmented services to emulate enterprise-style architecture.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Components</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>pfSense/OPNsense firewall</li>
        <li>Layer-3 managed switch</li>
        <li>VLAN segmentation (Servers, IoT, Guest, Management)</li>
        <li>DNS & DHCP infrastructure</li>
        <li>Site-to-site and remote access VPN</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Goals</h2>
    <p>
        Security, scalability, and replicating real production networks.
    </p>
